<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType"> altar-stele</rs>, with moulding above and below (H. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.88</measure>, W. <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.43</measure>, D. <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.38</measure>). The relief is of a heavily armed <rs type="decoration">gladiator</rs>, with a short sword in right hand, a long shield in the left, and a crested helmet, advancing to the right.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the upper moulding, which is broken</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>lunate sigma and ?epsilon; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.035</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date>(<rs type="criteria">content</rs>, <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)
</p>
</div>
